5 minutes to fry a pork chop? It wasn't cooked in the middle. I grilled it for another 5.
It seemed a lot of messing about and I'm not convinced the ingredients all go together. The red onion adds crunch (not fully cooked) and the blue cheese did absolutely nothing at that volume.
If I were to try again it would all be in the oven.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-100679"><a id="comment-100679"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">Lay Di</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 27th Oct, 2011</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Left out the cheese and added some garlic butter instead</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-98884"><a id="comment-98884"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">pleonast</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 10th Oct, 2011</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivest